text.tspan: Two main characters in Boys Love is Noeru and Mamiya.
Mamiya is a magazine editor who is sent to interview Noeru,
who is a high school student and good-looking teen model.
During the interview, Mamiya accidentally touches a topic of
Noeruâ€™s difficult memory. The action irritates Noeru, and he
decides to punish Mamiya through his celebrity power and
sexual conquest. Mamiya does his best to avoid falling into
his trap. Through their interactions, they begin to know each
other better and start to develop a strong bond.
This art work follows the traditional Yaoi manga style which
talks about how two male characters develop a romantic re
lationship for each other with Noeru as seme (aggressor) and
Mamiya as uke (submissive). The manga involves sex
scenes but gives no descriptions on details.
